st reliable quantity to be compared\nwith observations and is the best estimator of the star formation timescale at\neach radius.(abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2005 10:29:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2005 10:35:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
