ct as well as the attenuation of\nextracellular potentials with distance. We suggest that induced electric fields\nin passive cells surrounding neurons is the physical origin of frequency\nfiltering properties of LFPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2005 20:11:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2006 21:09:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-16"}
